RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT REMITTANCE_REF_NO from txtb_tax_remittance_master where sypks_utils.get_branch(REMITTANCE_REF_NO) = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH
SELECT O.AC_GL_NO, O.AC_GL_DESC FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT O WHERE O.ac_gl_rec_status='O' And O.AUTH_STAT = 'A' order by AC_GL_NO
select trn_code, trn_desc from oltms_trn_code where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A' order by trn_code
select mis_group, group_desc from mitms_mis_group where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A' order by mis_group
select ccy_code,ccy_name from cytms_ccy_defn where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A' order by ccy_code

RAD_SUMMARY.TITLE: LBL_TAX_REMITANCE_SUMMARY
RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: sypks_utils.get_branch(REMITTANCE_REF_NO) in (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID)
